{"tid":1820152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【開定】對台灣國民黨「沉默的少數派」嘅咀咒","createTime":"2020-01-11T11:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T11:26:53.000Z","uid":131691,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbafa15e7a0d54e8a9277a420ba1fbf95cc4ad1","tid":1820152,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExkOzMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExkOzMU.jpg&h=bf53ab21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqMFqTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqMFqTz.jpg&h=707eaa9c&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n親中嘅國民黨，賣台嘅國民黨，<br />\n不論有意定無意，出於利益定係弱智，上<br />\n至韓國瑜，下至一批「沉默的少數派」，一批「韓粉」，<br />\n都要因爲你嘅選擇而受苦。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">VSOR, DILAPIDATOR, TENTATORE, SOMNIATORE, DEVORATOR, CONCISOR, ET SEDUCTOR. O all ye ministers and companions, I direct, conjure, constrain and command you to fulfil this behest willingly, namely, straightway to consecrate this image, which is to be done in the name of Saturn, that as the face of the one is contrary to the other, so the same may never more look upon another.</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我以  撒頓，朱比特之父  嘅名，我咀咒：<br />\n願  韓粉傾家蕩產，<br />\n願  國民黨滅黨，<br />\n願  韓國瑜橫屍街頭。<br />\n<br />\n以  撒頓，朱比特之父  第四個五角星，我爲以上人士帶嚟毀滅。</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VO4cg4D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVO4cg4D.gif&h=4a704ea7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Where are ye, SOMNIATOR, VSOR, DILAPIDATOR, TENTATOR, DIVORATOR, CONCISOR, SEDUCTOR, ye who sow discord, where are you? Ye who infuse hatred and propagate enmities,<br />\n<br />\nI conjure you by him who hath created you for this ministry, to fulfill this work, in order that whenever Saturn shall eat of like things, or shall touch them, in whatsoever manner, never shall he go in peace.</span></em><br />\n<br />\n禮成。"},{"pid":"b133ff49abed8508c6f6511449882b3ebbb4f937","tid":1820152,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=ec9c8997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span>"},{"pid":"09bb488ab792ab1540a4a6856f71b23897ada470","tid":1820152,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8282ee69b4bb7b4298fa6ccfbf9b0aab2d32ada","tid":1820152,"uid":293677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通匪台奸</span></span><br />\n必需制裁"},{"pid":"95c9c03adc0c16dca5dd068b5e3bed240c6954a0","tid":1820152,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"sorry巴打唔係好明個詛咒嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪羅馬帝國定希臘時期嘅嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36168162acff7057200ff7b3c6e9ef331c014d92","tid":1820152,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95c9c03adc0c